  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Somalia: Enhancing the Capacity of Justice Institutions to Deliver Justice in Somalia</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">1) To develop institutional framework for legal skills, strengthen harmonization of national laws and improve forensic science activities in Puntland. 2) To improve application of procedures and practices, by judges and prosecutors, in accordance with principles of the Constitution and international human rights standards. 3) To improve accessibility of the Attorney General Offices in Federal Member States.</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="3">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Direct beneficiaries: the Judiciary and prosecutors. Indirect beneficiaries: justice seekers and the Somali people.</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="2">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The project aims to improve access to formal justice for all Somalis, including vulnerable groups.</narrative>
  </description>
